snippet.title: Mad's Tech
snippet.description:
This channel is a mixture of reviews, information and support on Drones, Radio Control and Tech. I try to provide content that help people make purchasing decisions and supports them with issues they may have. I also offer help and support across Facebook, RC Groups and other forums.

Support Us On Patreon  - https://www.patreon.com/MadRC


=============================
Review & Business Enquiries:
=============================

Review Enquiries - If you would like to work with us on product or service you have please email mad_rc@icloud.com

Business Enquiries & Consulting - We have huge amount of experience in emerging technology and unmanned systems, we offer both in-house technical services and consultancy, if you would like to discuss how I can help you please email awuas@icloud.com 

=============================
Follow Me On Social Media
=============================
Twitter: @madrc1 
Instagram: ian_mads_tech
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Themadrc1/
